extends layout.pug

block content 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-intro
    div

      //- Heading for project gallery 
      h1 Potential employers and collaborators: enjoy some samples of my work!

      //- Description of the purpose of portfolio website and projects contianed in it 

      p.lead.text-light
        | Below is a compilation of the projects I've created to
        | demonstrate knowledge of the programming skills I have learned.
        br
        | Additionally, the creation of this very website is a project assignment
        | designed to prove an understanding of key development tools through use of 
        | node and express, as well as showcase
        | many of the foundational concepts presented and built upon throughout the course program thus far. 

  article.grid-container.portfolio-index
    
    .grid-x.grid-margin-x.small-up-2.medium-up-2.large-up-3

      //- Pug `each` iterator creates a project img, title and link in the markup for each of the projects in gallery.  
      
      //- a combination of interpolation and template literals used to dynamically generate the the routes in the href, as well as the img's src and the projects title.
      each project in projects
        .cell
          a(href= `projects/${project.id}`)
            image.thumbnail(src=`${project.image_urls[3]}`)
            h5= project.project_name
      

   
      
